  "text": "To identify the main biological processes targeted by CpG ODN and a-GalCer, gene annotations were retrieved to identify GO terms. The level of significance of each GO term was evaluated using a reporter algorithm [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] to map the GO terms (expressed as Q-values of transcriptome data). Hierarchical clustering based on significant Q-values of GO terms belonging to biological processes was performed to cluster response patterns induced by the two adjuvants ( Fig. 2A and Figure S2 ).",
